  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Retail Assistant",
  "description": "<p>This role requires you to be on-site.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are operating a Retail Shop for Dryclean &amp; Laundry Services.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Responsibilities include the following</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Manage Sales Transactions, Opening &amp; Closing Balance</li>\n  <li>Opening / Closing of Shop</li>\n  <li>Servicing Customers to collect &amp; return laundry</li>\n  <li>Basic Retail Administrative works (e.g recording invoices, refunds, items received etc..)</li>\n  <li>Perform General Basic Cleaning of shop (To keep the shop tidy &amp; clean, it is a small shop)</li>\n</ol>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Moderately good level of Spoken &amp; Written English</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of how to operate POS Systems</li>\n  <li>Able to work on weekends &amp; PH apart from weekdays.</li>\n  <li>Be able to travel to the Head Office &amp; Factory in the west once or twice a year for training or discussions</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Good to have:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Experience in customer facing roles</li>\n  <li>Knowledge in simple troubleshooting of Electronic Tablet for POS System</li>\n  <li>Enjoys interacting with people</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Location, Hours &amp; Other Information</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Compass One - North / North East Region (Inter-Outlet travel will be required in the future if there are expansions, for now it is not required)</li>\n  <li>5 Days per week, 10:45am - 9:15pm (Shop operating hours are from 11am to 9pm with an hour's break inbetween).</li>\n  <li>Salary is based assuming on taking on a full time position with the indicated work days and hours.</li>\n</ul>",
